Package org.qualitune.naoservice.client

Interface Summary
NaoConstants Provides constants used by the NaoUtil class.
 

Class Summary
Nao Java abstraction layer for Nao humanoid robot.
Nao.ALAudioDevice The ALAudioDevice module allows other modules to access to the sound data of the nao's microphones, and to send sound toward its loudspeakers The way to receive or send the audio data depends whether the modules are local (dynamic library) or remote (executable).
Nao.ALAudioPlayer This module allows to play wav and mp3 files on NAO
Nao.ALAudioSourceLocalization This module computes the position (azimuth, elevation) of a sound source detected by ALSoundDetection.
Nao.ALBehaviorManager This module is intended to manage behaviors.
Nao.ALBluetooth This module handle one or several Aldebaran's bluetooth boards.
Nao.ALBonjour The bonjour module advertises this Nao's IP address on the local network using the bonjour protocol.
Nao.ALFaceDetection ALFaceDetection is the Module which detects faces.
Nao.ALFaceTracker This module is dedicated to Track a Face expressed in NAO_SPACE.
Nao.ALFileManager ALFileManager manages the user files stored in a shared folder.
Nao.ALFrameManager Frame manager is used to play choregraphe projects in naoqi.
Nao.ALFsr Deals with FSR sensors.
Nao.ALInfrared This module works with Linux Infrared Remote Control (LIRC) in order to emit/receive IR remotes keys or to emit/receive IR information to/from an other Nao.
Nao.ALLandMarkDetection ALLandMarkDetection is a module which detects and recognizes Naomarks.
Nao.ALLaser Allow control over Hokuyo laser when available on Nao's head.
Nao.ALLauncher ALlauncher allows to link dynamicaly with library, run executable, unload library, check if module is loaded...
Nao.ALLeds ALLeds contains helper methods for controlling the Light Emiting Devices (LEDs).
Nao.ALLogger This module allows you log errors, warnings, and info to syslog, stdout or a file.
Nao.ALMemory ALMemory is a class that implements an event-based storage base.
Nao.ALMotion ALMotion provides methods that help make Nao move.
Nao.ALMotionRecorder ALMotionRecorder is a module giving the possibility to record Nao's motors poses.
Nao.ALPreferences ALPreferences allows access to xml preference files.
Nao.ALPythonBridge This module evaluates python commands on the fly.
Nao.ALRedBallDetection ALRedBallDetection is a module which can detect red ball based on color saturation.
Nao.ALRedBallTracker This module is dedicated to Track a Red Ball expressed in NAO_SPACE.
Nao.ALResourceManager Manage robot resources: Synchronize movement, led, sound.
Nao.ALRobotPose This module give the estimated Nao PoseDetects.
Nao.ALSensors Deals with bumpers and chest button.
Nao.ALSentinel ALSentinel (ex-ALWatchDog) is a module that implements vital services for Nao:
Nao.ALSonar Deals with Ultrasonic sound Sensors.
Nao.ALSoundDetection This module detects in incoming audio buffers every sound with a significative level.
Nao.ALSpeechRecognition ALSpeechRecognition gives access to the embedded voice recognition system.
Nao.ALTextToSpeech This module handles the text to speech operations.
Nao.ALVideoDevice ALVideoDevice, formerly called Video Input Module (V.I.M.), is architectured in order to provide every module related to vision, called Generic Video Module (G.V.M.), a direct access to raw images from video source, or an access to images transformed in the requested format.
Nao.ALVisionRecognition ALVisionRecognition is a module which detects and recognizes learned pictures, like pages of a comic books, faces of objects or even locations.
Nao.ALVisionToolbox This module contains different vision functionalities, like picture taking, video recording, white balance setting, etc ...
Nao.DCM Manage link with devices (sensors and actuators).
NaoData  
NaoJointInfo  
NaoJointInfos Class that contains infos of all Joints within the Nao.
NaoUtil This class provides further utility methods for the Nao class that cannot be generated from the NaoQi API (i.e., more complex requests).
SayParameter Class which can be used to pass parameters to the NaoUtil#say(Nao, String, SayParameter...) method.
 

Enum Summary
NaoJointID The ids for Joints that exist within a Nao.
 

Exception Summary
NaoUtilException Exception thrown if a request issued to a nao service fails.
